<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">م ز ر:</span> <span class="c2">(الْمِزْرُ)</span> بِالْكَسْرِ ضَرْبٌ مِنَ الْأَشْرِبَةِ.<span class="c5"> قَالَ ابْنُ عُمَرَ رَضِيَ اللَّهُ عَنْهُمَا:</span> هُوَ مِنَ الذُّرَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>